dataset.name: 当前日期
dataset.sql: select Datename(year,GetDate())+'-'+Datename(month,GetDate())+'-'+Datename(day,GetDate()) as dateTime;

dataset.name: 案卷统计swhyda-bgqx
dataset.sql: SELECT bgqx, COUNT(DISTINCT ajh) as count FROM swhyda WHERE (bgqx = '长期' or bgqx = '永久') and sxh = '001' GROUP BY bgqx;

dataset.name: 卷内文件统计swhyda-bgqx
dataset.sql: SELECT bgqx,COUNT(*) as count from swhyda WHERE ys not like '%[^0-9]%' and (bgqx = '长期' or bgqx = '永久') GROUP BY bgqx ORDER BY bgqx;
